0.3 series
- Initial usable version. 
- Major features: character sheets, power cards, custom dice and a glossary.

0.4.0
- Support for latest, stable Foundry release.
- Power macros - see MacroAPI.d.ts for the DSL.
- Improved tooltips which display HTML and don't underlap the sidebar.
- Sheet UI tweaks.
- Power cards now fit into smaller spaces such as the default chatlog. Power messages in the chat log can be popped out into their own window.